HISTORY

02 Apr 2026

Fixed

    CODERUN.CGI $ERRF was (just) ERRF.

Added

    CODERUN.CGI "cmd" to exec a program into the textarea; also for this 
    QRY.SH, HTM.SH. Also, re-arrainged some HTML controls.

23 Mar 2026

Fixed

    CODERUN.CGI tests the run/compile error file not just for existence but for 
    esisting and non-zero size.

Changed

    Moved all the calls to the Modules/API into CODERUN.CGI.
    Moved CFG configuration functionality into DAT.SH. (Form data save/load 
    still in CFG.SH).
    

21 Mar 2026

Good Enough to be called v2.0. (Though I am lax when it comes to really 
tracking the version/changes.)

Major changes (CODERUN.CGI) for more supporting more compiled languages; added 
"NEW" and "LOAD" commands to include language examples code and loading code 
from the temporary files. Cleaned-up the inerface.

Added

    DAT.SH: Holds data for default language examples.

Changed

    BIN.SH      Added some language DATA.
    CFG.SH      Removed some unused code.
    QRY.SH      "
    SRV.SH      "
    HTM.SH      Re-designed the HTML for clarity.

19 Mar 2026

Changed BIN.SH data "tmp" to "type" (filename type), and added in CORERUN.CGI:

    $tmp=$type.tmp

16 Mar 2026

Added support for Go Language.

In File BIN.SH:

    [go]
    bin "go run"
    tmp tmp.go
    name Go
    desc "Go Lang"
    pre "package main;"

In File CODERUN.CGI:

    if [[ $env ]]; then
        export "$env"
    fi

(Support for env was added for Go, but then Go wants more than one... So 
instead of more code, I just decided to update the requirements that Go 
needs a proper environment.)
